To create "digital toast" components using the <details> and <summary> elements, we can combine Bootstrap’s utility classes for spacing, borders, and shadows with custom CSS to handle the "slide down" animation.

This approach treats the <summary> as the toast header and the remainder of the <details> content as the toast body.

